########### Linear Regression Approaches: Logistic Regression ########### 

#Definition of a logistic regression model 
lr_model<- logistic_reg() %>%
  # Set the engine
  set_engine("glm") %>%
  # Set the mode
  set_mode("classification") %>%
  # Fit the model with the train data
  fit(Arrest~., data = df_train)
